        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">It would have to cause no agro to the necro or it wouldn't be of much use.  Basically, the inverse of Concussion and Jolt spells..</P><P><BR>Couldn't this type of spell be a unique necro ability that would make us wanted more?  </P><P>Hate increase could come in different forms.. Single target, top of hate list increase only, single target EVERYONE on list gets bumped up, or AE versions of the above.  </P><P>Example of an AE version in use:</P><P>Monk pulls and feigns.  big fat ogre warrior chains say, 4 mobs off the monks feign.  All mobs start beating on the warrior.. Necro casts this AE hate spell, making all the mobs hate the warrior more.  Chanter can then mez away without mobs going after him, clerics could heal that warrior and the mobs wouldn't jump the cleric.</P><P>Obviously this could become too powerfull, but verant would just have to balance it correctly.  This type of spell should be "stackable" also.. so muleiple necros = more and faster hate increases.  A handful of necros might then be wanted badly on a big raid to keep a mob on the main tank.</P><P></P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
